prodNameC: 常盈白蛋白免疫試驗系統
ingredientsDesc:
Anti-albumin antibody-coated tubes: 2 x 50 tubes
125I-labeled albumin: one 55 mL vial
The vial contains 300 kBq, at the date of manufacture, of 125I-labeled albumin in buffer containing bovine serum albumin, sodium azide (＜0.1%). and a dye.
Albumin dilution buffer (4x): one 25 mL vial
The solution contains bovine serum albumin and sodium azide (＜0.1%).
Calibrators: six 0.5 mL vials
The calibrator vials contain from 0 to 150 mg/L of albumin in buffer containing bovine serum albumin and sodium azide(＜0.1%).
Control sample: one 0.5 mL vial
The vial contains albumin in buffer containing bovine serum albumin and sodium azide.
